      stall: { text: "The reinforced stall. The scratch marks inside go inches deep into oak - made over years, and from the height of them, by something that grew. In the corner, placed with care on a small pile of bones: a child's straw doll. On the damp inner walls, a pale crust has bloomed - saltpeter, enough to matter to the right sort of mind.", finds: ["saltpeter"], again: "The doll watches over the bones. You leave the arrangement be - some things are shrines whether or not anyone says so." },
      "tack room": { text: "Rotted bridles, split saddles - and beneath the wreckage, the useful survivors: a coil of rope still sound, and a set of leather armor made for a rider who never came back for it.", finds: ["rope", "leather_armor"] },
